songs.title: Boo’d Up (T-Mix)
songs.lyrics:
[Intro: T-Pain]

It's a T-Mix, baby

But I know you be creepin', girl, I see you tonight (yeah)
Just give me 30 minutes, baby, I'll be on the way (I'm on the way)
